Class whosLateController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.Controller
      • controllers.whosLateController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class whosLateController
extends Controller
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Controller for the print of Flight that are late A table with all the Flights that have ending rent day anterior to today's date are displayed in the middle of this window Extends the Controller class to get the data required for the action and to communicate with other windows
